<item>
            <title>[CAMEL-9122] Ruby script cannot access request object</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CAMEL-9122</link>
                <project id="12311211" key="CAMEL">Camel</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;with script&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;body = $request.getBody()
$request.setBody(&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;Hello &quot;&lt;/span&gt; + body);
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;we get &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;uby: body = $request.getBody();
$request.setBody(&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;Hello &quot;&lt;/span&gt; + body);. Cause: org.jruby.embed.EvalFailedException: (NoMethodError) undefined method `getBody&apos; &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;for&lt;/span&gt; nil:NilClass
