                            <comment id="14910079" author="davsclaus" created="Mon, 28 Sep 2015 06:28:14 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Lets keep 1.7.18 on this release, and maybe there is a working jruby release in the future.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
